pol:EU_32018R1999_Title_0_Chapter_5_Section_3_Article_32_Paragraph_1 a pol:LegalActParagraph ;
    pol:text "Where the Commission concludes, on the basis of the assessment carried out in accordance with Article 29(1) and (2), that progress towards achieving the Union's energy and climate objectives is insufficient, it shall propose measures and exercise its powers at Union level to ensure that those objectives are met." .

