    pol:text "Where a Member State's share of energy from renewable sources falls below one or more of its national reference points in 2022, 2025 and 2027 as referred to in point (a)(2) of Article 4, it shall take within one year additional measures such as those set out in points (a) to (e) of the first subparagraph of this paragraph sufficient to cover the gap." .

